Istockhomes makes no guarantees regarding:
- fitness for a particular purpose
- uptime
- performance
- commercial success

Use of the software is at your own risk.

---

## Termination

This licence may be terminated if its terms are violated.

Termination affects platform access and connectivity, not ownership of your independent design assets.

---

## Intent

This licence exists to encourage:
- creativity
- real businesses
- fair participation
- long-term alignment

It is not intended to trap developers, but it **does protect the platform**.

